E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux/2020-12-10_16-35-43.png\" alt=\"2020-12-10_16-35-43\"></p>\n<p>这里我没有选中”安装Ubuntu时下载更新“，这样会安装的时间会加长。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2021/01/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8VMware%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux/2020-12-10_16-38-22.png\" alt=\"2020-12-10_16-38-22\"></p>\n<p>这里清除的意思是虚拟机清除，不用害怕自己电脑清除掉。</p>\n<p>点击”现在安装“即可开始安装</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2021/01/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8VMware%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux/2020-12-10_16-42-33.png\" alt=\"2020-12-10_16-42-33\"></p>\n<p>选个时区，选择上海就可以了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2021/01/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8VMware%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux/2020-12-10_16-45-27.png\" alt=\"2020-12-10_16-45-27\"></p>\n<p>以下内容自己去设置吧，可以随便填写。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2021/01/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8VMware%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux/2020-12-10_16-47-02.png\" alt=\"2020-12-10_16-47-02\"></p>\n<p>接下来就是安装了，比较漫长，去打个游戏吧。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2021/01/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8VMware%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux/2020-12-10_16-49-21.png\" alt=\"2020-12-10_16-49-21\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"重启\"><a href=\"#重启\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"重启\"></a>重启</h2><p>安装完毕后Ubuntu会重启，<strong>注意</strong>一定要把<strong>”光盘取出来“</strong>，意思是说在光盘那里取消选项”启动时连接“，之后再重新开机。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2021/01/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8VMware%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux/2020-12-10_18-29-25.png\" alt=\"2020-12-10_18-29-25\"></p>\n<p>开机后基本就可以正常运行了。</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"linux","path":"api/categories/linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"linux","path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"安装","path":"api/tags/安装.json"}]}